</p>
<p>This is the User object for <em>who</em> is currently logged in. I'll add some inline documentation
to show that.</p>
<p>When the user submits the payment form, there are <em>two</em> different scenarios. First,
<code>if (!$user-&gt;getStripeCustomerId())</code>, then this is a first-time buyer, and we need
to create a new Stripe Customer for them:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="082b523d67">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
