<p>So we can easily look up a user in Stripe's dashboard later.</p>
<p>The <em>really</em> important field is <code>source</code>. This refers to the <em>payment source</em> -
so credit or debit card in our case - that you want to attach to the customer. Set
this to the <code>$token</code> variable:</p>
