<h2 id="charging-the-user">Charging the User <a class="headerlink" href="stripe-customers#charging-the-user" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>The last thing we need to update is the Charge: instead of passing <code>source</code>, charge
the <em>customer</em> instead. Set <code>'customer' =&gt; $user-&gt;getStripeCustomerId()</code>:</p>
